{"id": "1366327293873488025", "channel_id": "1366327293873488025", "type": 0, "author_id": "233903186048581632", "author_name": ".alice13th", "author_bot": false, "content": "Greetings Developers.\n\nI am the admin from the fan page \"Morimens Thailand.\" Recently, I have received considerable feedback from many Thai players regarding concerns about the fairness of the Self-Select Awakening Event banner. \n\nCombining both Awaker and Wheel of Destiny into a single banner has been perceived as highly inappropriate, particularly for new and mid-level players who have not been playing since day one.\n\nFor example, some players have invested all their resources trying to pull for Awaker they would like to have but  got rate-off item from the banner. \n\nThe real issue arises when the game grants them double or even tripple Wheel of Destiny cards consecutively at pity rate but no Awaker. This has been extremely discouraging for many newer players, to the extent that some have even declared their intention to quit the game.\n\nHere are some suggestions/feedback I would like to propose:\n\n- Separate the Awaker and Wheel of Destiny into different banners, similar to the usual event banners \n\nor\n\n- If a player receives either an Awaker or Wheel of Destiny within the first 90 rolls, the following 90 rolls should guarantee the other item they have not yet obtained. After both have been received, the system can then randomize between Awaker and Wheel of Destiny starting from 270 rolls onward.\n\nI sincerely hope that the team will take our feedback into consideration. This is the first game that I have felt treats both free-to-play and paying players fairly and respectfully. \n\nI truly wish for the game to continue preserving this strength, just as it has since the early days when I first started playing.\n\nBest Regards", "timestamp": "2025-04-28T08:16:51.993000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-04-28T08:23:46.884000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 23}, {"emoji": "☝️", "emoji_id": null, "count": 32}], "attachments": [{"id": "1366327294251106354", "filename": "493970682_611717601918210_1577188363390136190_n.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 247615, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1366327293873488025/1366327294251106354/493970682_611717601918210_1577188363390136190_n.jpg?ex=6a003ef4&is=69feed74&hm=3b4efc0b46bfec3268a75bc69a878d47ff4edf065d7eb258dc5446f99432b2ed&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1366327293873488025", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "[Suggesion] [Feedback] About Unfair Self-Select Awakening Event", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1361168939622727801", "1361169005435420785"]}
